  "title": "Financial Controller",
  "description": "<p><strong>Our Client:</strong></p><ul><li>Up to $10,000, and VB</li><li>Office Hours, 9am - 6pm</li><li>Geylang</li><li>Engineering Industry</li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Work with internal teams to manage monthly cash flow and financial forecasts.</li><li>Review and compare actual expenses with the budget, collaborating with QS and HR.</li><li>Find the best deals for bonds and insurance for projects.</li><li>Plan and monitor foreign currency needs, minimizing forex risk.</li><li>Coordinate with the corporate secretary and communicate with bankers, insurance companies, and regulators.</li><li>Work with internal teams to provide financial advice and support decision-making.</li><li>Prepare and submit monthly reports on financial status, banking facilities, foreign currency, and other key metrics.</li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Bachelor’s degree in Finance.</li><li>min 10 years of experience preferred.</li><li>Experience in Engineering industry.</li></ul><p></p><p>For interested applicants, please click \"Quick Apply”</p><p></p><p>We regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates would be notified.</p><p></p><p>By submitting your personal data and/or resume, you will be deemed to have agreed and consented to us collecting, using, retaining, and disclosing your personal information to prospective employers for their consideration.</p><p></p><p>Elsa Adam | EA Reg No: R22109576</p><p>JTE Recruit Pte Ltd | EA Lic No: 14C7215</p><p></p>",
